{"word":"G1825 - ἐξεγείρω - exegeírō - ex-eg-i'-ro - Raise up","slug":"G1825","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξεγείρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>exegeírō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ex-eg-i'-ro"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Raise up"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BE;&#x03B5;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C9; - exegeiro&#x0304;</b> - <i>ex-eg-i'-ro</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1453\">G1453</a>; to <i>rouse fully</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>resuscitate</i> (from death), <i>release</i> (from infliction): - raise up."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1127\">G1127</a>, <a href=\"#/G1453\">G1453</a>, <a href=\"#/G1454\">G1454</a>"}]}